parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the ABS system can cause extended stopping distances, loss of control, and accidents, which can lead to injuries or fatalities.
symptoms: The brake pedal goes to the floor
the vehicle slides to a stop
the ABS system engages and then disengages
the check engine light illuminates on the instrument panel.

parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the windshield wiper motor can cause intermittent or complete loss of windshield wiper function, reducing driver visibility and increasing the risk of a vehicle crash, especially in inclement weather.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: EGR Valve Clogging and Fuel Pressure Regulator Issues
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The clogging of the EGR valve and potential failure of the fuel pressure regulator can cause the engine to sputter and stall, leading to a loss of power and control, which can increase the risk of accidents.

the EGR valve needs frequent cleaning.
